BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:9tTzTGM9Ps_-MnNcG6V2_
SUMMARY:The Insidious Trilogy: A THEATRICAL EVENT
DTSTAMP:20260325T212655Z
DTSTART:20260522T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:The centerpiece of the season will be the complete Insidious Tr
	ilogy . The Trilogy contemplates Jim Crow\, its history\, and its contempo
	rary manifestations\; it confronts America’s history of racial violence\, 
	systemic oppression\, and deliberate forgetting. It is not merely a series
	 of dances—it is a cultural intervention. The three works that make up the
	 trilogy are Strange Fruit\, Grief\, and Targeted. PERFORMANCE SCHEDULE Pl
	ease note that each performance day will present various works from the In
	sidious Trilogy. The complete Trilogy performs over five days in a 2-act o
	r 3-act rotating repertory format: Wed. May 20\, 2026: Strange Fruit\, Gri
	ef (two acts) Thur. May 21\, 2026: Strange Fruit\, Targeted (two acts) Fri
	. May 22\, 2026: Targeted\, Grief (two acts) Sat.\, May 23\, 2026: Strange
	 Fruit\, Grief\, and Targeted ( three acts\, with a dinner break ) Sun. Ma
	y 24\, 2026: Targeted\, Grief (two acts) GROUP & DISCOUNT TICKETS We belie
	ve dance should be accessible to all\, which is why we offer a variety of 
	discounts and flexible pricing options to all performances: $25 Tickets ar
	e available for groups of 5 or more adults. Enter the following code at ch
	eckout: GROUP Dance For All tickets are open to everyone at a discounted r
	ate of $10 per person. Pay-What-You-Can (PYWC) tickets ensure everyone can
	 experience our performances\, no matter their budget. These tickets are a
	vailable on a first-come\, first-served basis\, and there is no minimum am
	ount required to reserve a ticket. Please email admin@spectrumdance.org to
	 reserve a PWYC ticket.\n\nhttps://web.ovationtix.com/trs/pe.c/36947\n\nFr
	om Spectrum Dance Theater
URL:https://web.ovationtix.com/trs/pe.c/36947
LOCATION:Spectrum Dance Theater\, 800 Lake Washington Blvd E\, Seattle\, WA
	 98122
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:spectrum-dance
CATEGORIES:Spectrum Dance Theater
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
END:VEVENT
